 \left(\frac{5}{6}\right)^{n-1}\cdot\left(\frac{1}{6}\right) 
 E[x]=\frac{1}{6}\cdot \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} n\left(\frac{5}{6}\right)^{n-1} 
 \frac{5}{6}E[x]=\frac{1}{6}\cdot \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} n\left(\frac{5}{6}\right)^n=\frac{1}{6}\sum_{n=2}^{\infty} (n-1)\left(\frac{5}{6}\right)^{n-1}=\frac{1}{6}\sum_{n=2}^{\infty}n\left(\frac{5}{6}\right)^{n-1}-\frac{1}{6}\sum_{n=2}^{\infty}\left(\frac{5}{6}\right)^{n-1} 
 =E[x]-\frac{1}{6}-\frac{1}{6}\cdot \frac{5}{6}\cdot\frac{1}{1-\frac{5}{6}}=E[x]-\frac{1}{6}-\frac{5}{6}=E[x]-1 
